Halfsegment - Class in stlib.datatypes.spatial.util
Class to represent 'Halfsegment' objects
Halfsegment() - Constructor for class stlib.datatypes.spatial.util.Halfsegment
Constructor for a empty and undefined 'Halfsegment' object.
Halfsegment(PointIF, PointIF, boolean) - Constructor for class stlib.datatypes.spatial.util.Halfsegment
Constructor to create a 'Halfsegment' object by passing the endpoints and a flag which indicate the dominating point of this segment
The passed points will be assigned to the internal leftPoint and rightPoint by the following rule:
leftPoint = min(p0, p1)
rightPoint = max(p0, p1)
Halfsegment(double, double, double, double, boolean) - Constructor for class stlib.datatypes.spatial.util.Halfsegment
